                    					<h3 id="page_title">13 Things Your Waiter Won&#8217;t Tell You</h3>
	<p class="dek">restaurant, waiter, restaurant horror stories,</p>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
<span class="single-title">From <i>Waiter Rant: Thanks for the Tip -- Confessions of a Cynical Waiter by The Waiter</i>  from <a href="http://www.rd.com/offer/rd/current/rdnavsubscribe.jsp?trkid=rdcom_article_top" rel="bookmark">Reader's Digest  | August 2008</a></span>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
